<br>
Sure, everyone gets pimped, no one is denying that.<br>
<br>
The problem is everyone wears the &quot;elemental uniform&quot; to start.  There are only a few really uber items, which tend to go to the few elite members of most guilds, as there really aren't enough to go around to a whole guild.  That leaves the rest of the members in a position where a new member can reach their gear lvl within a week or 2 of joining an elemental guild and it means that they go the entire expansion without ever receiving the first of an item, or some particularly uber drop.  It just makes you feel very unspecial and ordinary.<br>
<br>
