<br>
If you give elemental legs to someone, which are rare, that means something.  If you give them the first elemental legs, it means even more.<br>
<br>
It's just how human nature works.<br>
<br>
The problem imo with PoP (at the elemental level) is that loot is divided into 2 categories.<br>
<br>
1) Uber stats but extremely common and thus not meaning much to the player who receives the item.  These are extremely common.<br>
<br>
2) Even more uber stats, but exceedingly rare, only a few players can get even one of these types of items (these are elemental god type drops, and not even all of them, only the best).<br>
<br>
The players that don't get the 2)'s, because there just aren't enough to go around, don't feel appreciated.<br>
<br>
